  Ti7 I-koan2 thiaN-tioh8 Ng5 Bou7-seng7 Sian-siN (hian7-si5 ti7 Ji7-chui2 e5 Ng5 Jin5-siu7 Bok8-su e5 lau7-pe7) kong2, ThiN-te7 e5 Chu2 na7 m7 pai3, chiu7 m7-bian2 pai3. Chit ku3 oe7 khek-tiau5 ti7 goa2 e5 sim, chiu7 koat-i3 sin3 Chu2. Chng-tiong bo5 lang5 sin3 Chu2, chiu7 ka-ki7 chit8 e5 tak8 le2-pai3 tiam7 tiam7 thau lai5 Chiong-hoa3 le2 pai3. Tioh8 kiaN5 tiam2 goa7 cheng e5 lou7, tiong-tau3-tng3 siong5-siong5 bo5 chiah8 ia7 bo5 lang5 chai; m7-bat ji7, put-ko3 gong7-gong7 le2-pai3. 
  Au7-lai5 ui7-tioh8 chin ai3 thak8 Lo5-ma2-ji7, siuN7 ai3 kap pai3 Siong7-te3 lang5 toa3; m7-bian2 chiN5 bo5 iau3-kin2, na7 e7-thang thak8 Lo5-ma2-ji7 chiu7 ho2. Niu5 Chiam5-tek, hian7-si5 ti7 Tang-mng5 e5 Niu5 Siu-tek Bok8-su e5 lau7-pe7, chiu7 ka7 goa2 in2 khi3 kap in tiuN7-lang5, (Niu5 Siu-tek Bok8-su e5 goa7-kong) toa3. Thau5-ke m7-na7 ka3 goa2 Lo5-ma2-ji7 bat to7-li2, koh kong2 bo5 chiN5 be7 eng7-tit, chiu7 chit8 goeh8 hou7 goa2 khou-goa7 gin5. Che ti7 tng-si5 si7 chin u7 chiN5. M7-na7 an2-ni, goa2 khi3 toa3 e5 si5, iau2 chin m7 chiaN5-lang5, thau5-ke eng7 chin ho2 hou7 goa2 chiah8, siong7-chhiaN2 chit8-jit8 hou7 goa2 chiah8 gou7-tng3; goa2 e5 sin-the2 chiu7 it-tit8 toa7-han3, ia7 it-tit8 pui5 koh iong2 khi2--lai5, piaN3-se3 cho3-kang ia7 be7 ia3-lan2. Lang5 long2 liah8-cho3 ki5-koai3. Toa3 hia 5 goeh8-jit8, Lo5-ma2-ji7 chiu7 long2 e7, thau5-ke be2 Seng3-keng kap Seng3-si sang3 goa2; goa2 chiu7 kap i saN-si5, chiu7 khi3 Tai5-tiong, Ta7-li2-khit, Khe-sim-pou si3-ke3 cho3 chhou-kang than3-chiah8, kiaN5 kau3-hia, than3-chiah8 kau3-hia. Tng-si5 pun2-hiuN e5 lang5 hui-siong5 gong5-ngiah8 kong2, goa2 chit8-e7 jip8-kau3 sin-the2 piN3 hiah iong2, koh soa3 kiaN5 u7 lou7. Hit-si5 pun2-hiuN e5 lang5 chio2 lang5 bat kau3 Tai5-tiong. In-ui7 lang5 na7 beh chhut-mng5 tioh8 poah8 u7 poe chiah kaN2; na7 bo5 chiu7 kiaN e7 chhiong--tioh8, soah--tioh8, hoan7--tioh8, thou2--tioh8, koh lou7-tiong siong5-siong5 u7 chhiuN2-kiap e5 gui5-hiam2. It-poaN e5 lang5 sit8-chai7 si7 kiaN5 bo5-lou7, kiaN-hiaN5 koe3-jit8, chin-chham2. Chong2-si7 goa2 chi2-u7 sin3 Chu2 chiu7 bo5 kiaN, chin chu7-iu5 si3-ke3 khi3; chai7 ti7 hit-si5 si7 chit8-kiaN7 ki5-su7. Ia7 goa2 kau3 tak8 sou2-chai7 chiu7 ai3 kong2 to7-li2 hou7 lang5 thiaN, bo5 kong2 tong3 be7-tiau5. 
