  Toa3 I-koan2 5 ni5 au7, Lan5 I-seng tng2-khi3 Eng-kok, goa2 ia7 si5. Khi3 Toa7-sia7, ti7 hia kiat-hun, chhe-ku7 ka7 goa2 nia2 chit8 e5 heng5-siong-pai5 hou7 goa2 khi3 be7 ioh8. Ho2 than3 si7 ho2 than3, m7-ku2 sim kan-khou2. In-ui7 tng-si5 e5 be7 ioh8-a2 gau5 phian3--lang5; Leng5-sng Sou-taN2 be7 cho3 Eng-kok e5 toa7 pou2-ioh8, phau3 chui2 chit8-e7 kun2, ka7 lang5 kong2, Li2 khoaN3, Eng-kok e5 pou2-ioh8, lat8 chin toa7...... Sou2-i2 ti7 tng-si5 be7 ioh8-a2 bo5 ho2 mia5-siaN. Goa2 be7 3 ni5 goa7, u7 chit8 jit8 tui3 Hong-goan5 kiaN5 tng2-lai5 Chiong-hoa3 e5 lou7-tiong (tng-si5 bo5 chhia), ki5-to2 Siong7-te3 ka7 goa2 oaN7 chit-giap8, chin tu2-ho2, lai5 kau3 Chiong-hoa3 tu2-tioh8 Lan5 I-seng, kio3 goa2 koh kap i toa3. Goa2 kong2, Goa2 i2-keng u7 bou2-kiaN2; i in3 kong2, Bo5 iau3-kin2, chiu7 kap i toa3. Hit-si5 33 hoe3, u7 Chhi5 Chu2-in, Ong5 Kim-ti5, Gou5 Bun5-liong5, Ng5 Chin3-ban7 kap Ong5 Kheng3-liong5 cho3 Lan5 I-seng e5 hak8-seng; ki5-tiong Chhi5 Chu2-in tauh8-tauh8 kap goa2 chhut-khi3 kong2 to7-li2. SaN ni5 au7, khoaN3-tioh8 Thai3-peng5-keng2 Ko Kim-seng Bok8-su chhut ti7 Kau3-hoe7-po3, beh bou7-chip8 Si3-chap8 jit8 oh8 e5 hak8-seng 7 mia5; sim-te2 ka-ki7 siuN7 kong2 bo5 bang7. Lam5-pou7 u7 pah-lian5 keng e5 kau3-hoe7, chiah beh keng2 7 mia5; goa2 iu7 bo5 hak8-bun7, koh ka-chok8 5 lang5 leh. Cheng5 bou2 siN chit8 e5 chiu7 si2, koh chhoa7 au7--e5. Ti7 I-koan2 3 ni5 ku2 siN 3 e5, u7 5 e5 thau5-chhui3, thai3 u7 hoat-tou7 thang thak8 sim2-mih8 oh8! Ong5 Kheng3-liong5 khoaN3-tioh8 goa2, toa7 siaN mng7, Li2 si7 bo5 thak8-tioh8 Kau3-hoe7-po3 lou3, beh koh toa3 chia kau3 ti7-si5? Goa2 in3 kong2, U7 to u7 le3, taN a7 iau2 u7 hoat-tou7.
  Hit-si5 Gou5 Chhiu-bi5 ia7 ti7 hia, i si7 Tai5-pak chut-giap8--e5, thiaN-tioh8 chiu7 kong2, ¡§Li2 kiam2 u7 ai3 khi3? Na7 ai3, goa2 bin5-a2-chai3 beh khi3 Tai5-lam5 ka7 goan2 ko-a2 kong2.¡¨ I hit-si5 tu2-chiah cho3 Siu3-iN5 tiaN7-tioh8 na7-tiaN7. Goa2 chiu7 in3 i ho2. Lan5 I-seng, I-seng-niu5 ia7 hoaN-hi2. Gou5 Chhiu-bi5 lai5 hoe5-tap kong2 ho2, goa2 chiu7 khi3 Thai3-peng5-keng2 kang2-sip8 40 jit8, u7 Ko Lo3-thau5, Ang5 Tiau5-thiu, Khou2 Chin3-hong tang5-oh8. Au7-lai5 chiu7 toa3 kau3-hoe7: Sin-chhi7, A-li2-kang2, Iam5-pou, Ka-gi7 Koe3-kau, Lim5-ki2-pou, SoaN-pa3, Lok8-moa5-san2, Chip8-chip8 kau3 Chui2-li2-kheN, Tek-san. 
